 médicament prescrit</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">LIPRESCCONDAPPL<a name=\"en-fr-note-scope-codes-LIPRESCCONDAPPL\"> </a></td><td>Conditions d’application de la ligne de prescription</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">LIPRESCLIBMED<a name=\"en-fr-note-scope-codes-LIPRESCLIBMED\"> </a></td><td>Libellé textuel du médicament prescrit</td></tr></table></div>"
